Installation:

    git clone https://github.com/enterit/dotvim.git

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Install fonts
On Linux
    git clone https://github.com/powerline/fonts.git
    cd fonts
    ./install.sh
